# Files agents should NOT read automatically. The Biotic database and any local data
# extracts must stay out of the model's context unless the user explicitly points to them.
# (Claude Code honours .claudeignore; other agents: treat this as the do-not-read list.)

*.rds
*.rda
*.RData
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal
*.sqlite
*.db
*.xml
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.csv
*.tsv
*.parquet
*.feather

data/
outputs/
output/
results/
private/
scratch/

# The database default location (outside the repo, listed for clarity)
# ~/IMR_biotic_BES_database/
